{"article_id":"HmO9ABukedvzTBSx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A federal judge in the US state of Texas has ruled","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that a key part of the Affordable Care Act","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"( ACA ) ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"better known as Obamacare ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"is unconstitutional .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Twenty states argued","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"the whole law was invalidated by a change in tax rules last year","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"which eliminated a penalty","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"for not having health insurance .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"President Donald Trump said","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"the ruling was great news for America .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"The law 's provisions will , however , remain in place","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"until an appeal is heard at the US Supreme Court .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"President Trump promised to dismantle Barack Obama 's landmark 2010 healthcare law ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"which was designed","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"to make medical cover affordable for the many Americans","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"who had been priced out of the market .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"despite his Republican Party having majorities in both the House of Representatives and the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"the ACA is still operating .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"However , in 2017 Congress did repeal the requirement","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"- the so-called individual mandate -","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that people buy health insurance","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"or pay a tax penalty .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Mr Trump took to Twitter","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"following the judge 's ruling in Texas .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"He also urged incoming Democratic Senate minority leader Chuck Schumer and Democratic Speaker of the House Nancy Pelosi to `` pass a STRONG law","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that provides GREAT healthcare '' .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"The ruling came a day before the deadline for Obamacare enrolment for the coming year .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Two Republicans","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"- Texas Attorney General Ken Paxton and his Wisconsin counterpart Brad Schimel","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"led the legal challenge .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Sitting in Fort Worth ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"US District Judge Reed O'Connor noted","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"that a $ 1.5tn tax bill","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"passed by Congress in 2017","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"eliminated the tax penalties","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"which anyone","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"who failed to obtain health insurance","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"had to pay .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"As the individual mandate was an `` essential '' element of the ACA ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"the whole of Obamacare was therefore unconstitutional ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Judge O'Connor said .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"his ruling was concerned with the intentions of the 2010 and 2017 Congresses .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"`` The former enacted the ACA .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"The latter sawed off the last leg","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"it stood on . ''","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Ms Pelosi described the ruling as `` cruel '' and `` absurd ''","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"it would be repealed .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"She said","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"it exposed `` the monstrous endgame of Republicans ' all-out assault on people with pre-existing conditions and Americans ' access to affordable health care '' .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"Mr Schumer , meanwhile , said","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"the ruling appeared `` to be based on faulty legal reasoning","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"and hopefully it will be overturned '' .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"if it was upheld in the higher courts","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"`` it will be a disaster for tens of millions of American families , especially for people with pre-existing conditions '' .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"The decision is almost certain to be challenged in the US Supreme Court .","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"White House spokeswoman Sarah Sanders said","depth":4},{"id":62,"text":"that the law would remain in place for the time being ,","depth":5},{"id":63,"text":"pending further legal developments .","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"Meanwhile , the White House called on Congress to replace Obamacare with an affordable healthcare system","depth":3},{"id":65,"text":"which protects people with pre-existing conditions .","depth":3},{"id":66,"text":"But other states have argued","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"that eliminating Obamacare would harm millions of Americans ,","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"and pending any appeal","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"the landmark health care law remains in place .","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"US Senate Democratic leader Chuck Schumer said :","depth":4},{"id":71,"text":"`` If this awful ruling is upheld in the higher courts ,","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"it will be a disaster for tens of millions of American families . ''","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":145,"left":136,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":120,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":85,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":83,"right":84,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":77,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":0,"right":76,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":75,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nucleari